caption.p: Epithelial or fibroblast cells are differently susceptible to chikungunya virus infection. ( a) Quantification of the viral RNA load by real-time qRT-PCR from the supernatants infected with SZ1050 with MOI of 0.1 at 0, 24, 48 and 72 h. ( b) Quantification of the viral RNA load by real-time qRT-PCR from the supernatants infected with SZ1239 with MOI of 0.1 at 0, 24, 48 and 72 h. ( c) Comparison of viral increasing fold in the supernatant between SZ1050 and SZ1239 at 24 h. p. i. ( d) Comparison of viral increasing fold in infected cells between SZ1050 and SZ1239 at 24 h. p. i
